&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will become a product expert!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The Account Executive position is a quota-carrying position; you will own the full sales cycle, managing your own account pipeline and contributing to the team’s pipeline.&lt;/li&gt;
