&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Brand &amp;amp; Marketing Design Team Lead&lt;/strong&gt; to join our marketing team to lead our internal design studio. You’ll be responsible for building and managing a team of designers, copywriter and animator delivering world-class creative assets that power everything from product launches to brand assets and our global websites. You’ll be responsible for all aspects of design from planning to execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a unique opportunity to shape the voice, look, and feel of one of the most exciting SaaS brands out there. If you thrive in fast-paced environments, love design and structures, know how to bring clarity to complexity. Someone that enjoys when great design meets a great story this role is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Set the creative bar and hold it.&lt;/strong&gt; Give direction, step in when something isn&#39;t working, fix it yourself. Visual direction here isn&#39;t a memo, it&#39;s a conversation that happens in the file.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the brand across every surface.&lt;/strong&gt; Website, landing pages, events, films, social, decks, employer brand. If Connecteam shows up somewhere visually, it comes through this team.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build the production infrastructure.&lt;/strong&gt; Briefing, review cycles, asset management, AI-assisted pipelines it’s the systems that let a lean studio produce at volume without cutting corners on craft.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bring generative AI into the actual workflow.&lt;/strong&gt; Not as an experiment but as a production tool. From: Midjourney, Figma AI or MCP, Higgsfield or other tools: compress timelines, multiply output, free up the team for decisions that require real judgment.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be the creative counterpart to the rest of the company.&lt;/strong&gt; Translate business briefs into creative and design that moves people. Understand what each team actually needs, not just what they ask for.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience &amp;amp; Skills:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;visionary design lead&lt;/strong&gt; with a proven track record of 5+ years leading creative design team, in SaaS or tech companies&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;hands-on design leader&lt;/strong&gt; not just managing, but also diving in when needed to guide visual direction and make things better.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;natural mentor and team builder&lt;/strong&gt; you’ve grown designers, built workflows, and know how to create a team dynamic where magic happens.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&

&lt;p&gt;Business Development Representative - Strategic Accounts&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Connecteam&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Connecteam is the leading platform for managing deskless teams, trusted by over 80,000 businesses worldwide.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We built Connecteam for real operators - the people running shifts, jobs, and teams across stores and sites. The kind of work that doesn’t happen behind a desk, and doesn’t have time for messy spreadsheets, scattered group chats, or tools that don’t talk to each other.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Connecteam brings daily operations and team communication into one intuitive app - from hiring and scheduling to training, tasks, and day-to-day coordination. It gives teams the clarity and control to run the day, shift after shift, job after job.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Backed by $220M+ from Insights Partners, Stripes, and Tiger Global, Connecteam is rapidly expanding worldwide - empowering frontline teams to work smarter, stay connected, and operate with greater efficiency.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Strategic Accounts team is responsible for helping Connecteam win the industries, brands, and partnerships that will define our next stage of growth. We operate like a startup within Connecteam - moving quickly, testing new ideas, and building repeatable go-to-market motions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role combines the best of two worlds. The majority of your time will be spent generating new business through outbound prospecting, primarily cold calling. You&#39;ll also regularly travel across the US to attend conferences, trade shows, customer events, and industry association meetings, where you&#39;ll represent Connecteam, build relationships with business owners and operators, and generate qualified opportunities through face-to-face conversations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll partner closely with experienced Account Executives, become an expert in your assigned industries, and play a direct role in helping Connecteam break into new markets and strategic accounts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;re competitive, curious, enjoy meeting new people, and want a role with both high ownership and real growth opportunities, we&#39;d love to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your primary responsibilities will include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Generate pipeline through outbound prospecting.&lt;/strong&gt; Build qualified meetings through cold calling, LinkedIn outreach, and thoughtful account research.&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Generate pipeline through conferences and events.&lt;/strong&gt; Represent Connecteam at industry conferences, trade shows, and customer events, turning conversations into qualified business opportunities.&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Research strategic accounts and industries.&lt;/strong&gt; Identify high-potential brands, map decision-makers, and uncover opportunities that shape our go-to-market strategy.&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Become an industry expert.&lt;/strong&gt; Develop a deep understanding of your assigned vertical by speaking with customers, prospects, and ecosystem partners.&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Win every sprint.&lt;/strong&gt; Consistently exceed meeting targets while contributing ideas that improve your team&#39;s strategy, messaging, and execution.&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
